## Secrets Management Issues

### Ansible Vault Decryption Failed

Symptoms: - “Decryption failed” error when running playbook - “Vault password incorrect” message

Cause: Wrong vault password or corrupted vault file

Diagnosis: ```bash # Try to view vault ansible-vault view /opt/ansible/vars/vault.yml # Enter password - if fails, password is wrong ```

Solution:

1. Verify vault password in Vaultwarden:

    Open Vaultwarden
    Find “Ansible Vault Password” entry
    Copy password

2. Update .vault_pass file: ```bash nano /opt/ansible/.vault_pass # Paste correct password chmod 600 /opt/ansible/.vault_pass ```

3. Test decryption: ```bash ansible-vault view /opt/ansible/vars/vault.yml # Should show decrypted contents ```

Prevention: Keep vault password backup in offline secure location

